#            * cargo-binstall (binary installer prompts)
#            * mitsuhiko's idasen-control (desk control)
#            * sugar (THIS — Candy Machine config prompts)
#            * 1,500+ Rust applications
#          sugar — 224+ stars on metaplex-foundation/sugar,
#          tens of thousands of NFT collections deployed via
